{
  "texts": [
    "However, previous works only focused on a simple scenario, with only limited types of tools to solve the problem (Shi et al., 2024; Li et al., 2024a; Tang et al., 2024).",
    "To approximate realistic clinical scenarios and evaluate the general capabilities of the agent in the medical field, we investigate existing public medical datasets and divide them according to the ability requirement of the agents.",
    "We built a benchmark term CAB, which contains five capacity dimensions and 18 tasks in total.",
    "The details about the definition of the five dimensions and the corresponding tasks can be found in Appendix B.",
    "Based on the proposed CAB, we develop a toolbox that contains 15 types of tools to enable agents to handle diverse tasks."
  ]
}